reviewText:
My daughter has told me yet again, just how much she loves this video!  She always has.  She has autism, and develops a fondness for certain movies and videos. We've moved a few times in the last 7 years, and we somehow lost it.  Now that we have another copy, she is just in her world, and watches it constantly.  I will definitely order more things from this bookstore.

Thanks so much :)
